node.text:
Repost from @conservationorg I’m super excited to be a part of this beautiful project. It is an honor. Mahalo @savethewavescoalition @surfconservation for protecting our waves Aloha j
—
“What do you think I can do to your currents, your coastlines, your climate? My requirements are simple. Stop stripping the forests that keep my water clean, stop filling the atmosphere with dead carbon and keep your plastic to yourself. Work with me now, before it’s too late. I’ll keep coming, I am the wave.”

Aquaman actor, Native Hawaiian and ocean sustainability advocate Jason Momoa (@prideofgypsies) joins Conservation International’s award-winning Nature is Speaking series as The Wave. #NatureisSpeaking

@savethewavescoalition @surfconservation @taylorsteele

node.title: Trailer // FUTURE PEOPLE: The Family of Donor 5114

node.text: i’ve worked really hard to support and be creative for the companies i love and believe in  it goes without saying that i have a massive passion for LEICA @leicacamerausa  the M2 present was unreal it’s my favourite film camera. but most importantly i got a personal note from the president ceo  unko mike that means just as much.  mahalo for the birthday wishes. and all my aloha to the leica team  @kiran.karnani  i’m very grateful aloha j

node.text: HAPPY BELATED BIRTHDAY @marshallamps_uk  MAHALO @joelmanan your a legend. all my gear got held up and sent back to canada.  FUCK.  no amps no speakers for my vinyl.  love u bro for making the trek to help me out.  @marshallamps_uk  check out the bluetooth line @marshallheadphones i travel everywhere with them.  i love music. need it everywhere.  trust me one of my essentials.  all my aloha j

node.text: happy last day of 41. BEST FRIEND  @brianandrewmendoza made it happen.  42 here we go  craziest year to date.  all ALOHA to you and yours  J.  PS i can’t believe i have my own harley line.  fucking awesome.  mahalo @harleydavidson  harley aloha shirt.  dedicated to my grandmother.  MABEL.  chhheeeehuuuuuuuu

node.text: i’d rather have a cold plunge then heat. but it’s the last day of 41 and aquaman 2 is kicking my ass. in a good way. times are changing. need to take care of myself a little more.  hydrate up  sweat it out. mahalo @wbpictures for supporting @mananalu.water and being on aquaman 2  getting rid of single use plastic is an obsession of mine.  mahalo to everyone trying to make a difference  all my aloha j. #poundit #pounddatmana
